embeds.title: Server Rules
embeds.description:
For @everyone ,
The below are the following rules for this discord server.

Rule 1
Rule 1 is the misuse of nicknames that files under the following:
(a) NSFW nicknames
(b) Inappropriate nicknames including swearing

Rule 2
Members must keep their personal details and their life a secret to prevent Identity Theft. This includes:
(a) Name
(b) Date of Birth
(c) Where you live

Rule 3
No inappropriate content is allowed under any circumstances. Please, You might need NSFW content. However, we do not. This rule includes:
(a) Swearing
(b) NSFW
(c) Hate Speech
(d) Political comments (there is an actual discord server for that)
(e) Antagonizing comments
(f) SPAM (i'd prefer steak, thanks)

Rule 4
English is the main language of this server - we do not understand other languages so please try to use English when possible.

Rule 5
Staff are allowed to moderate at discretion. if you notice any activity which violates discord community guidelines and our rules report to them. 
If one of the staff are breaking these rules report that to <@!656478684315910163> or one of the <@&764368162669723657>. 

Rule ‚àû
Don't break these rules - offenders may be muted, kicked, softbanned or banned entirely depending on the situation and the total amount of offences.

Please do take notice that these rules will be subject to change.

**Want special perks?** Join our [server](https://discord.gg/xxnGus7qWr) and then [donate](https://www.buymeacoffee.com/Oxygen2Team)

embeds.title: Help
embeds.description:
Here is a list of commands that have currently been added to the bot

**fun**
 `fact` - Get any random fact
`meme` - Get a random meme

**moderation**
 `ban` - Remove a user from your server
`clear` - Remove messages from your server
`kick` - Remove a user from you server. No messages are removed and they can still get in.
`softban` - Remove a user, delete messages and they can still come back

**utilities**
 `create` - Create a text channel
`invite` - Get the bot invite code
`ping` - Poke me... I poke you back
`run` - Remove a user, delete messages and they can still come back
`scan` - Scan a URL
`stats` - Stare at the numbers of the bot
